# ===========================================
# Git LFS Setup Guide (if using LFS)
# ===========================================
#
# To track large files with Git LFS, run these commands:
# git lfs track "*.h5"
# git lfs track "*.hdf5"
# git lfs track "*.parquet"
# git lfs track "*.model"
# git lfs track "*.bin"
# git lfs track "data/*.csv"  # for large CSV files in data folder
#
# This creates/updates .gitattributes file which SHOULD be committed
# The .gitattributes file tells Git LFS which files to handle

